<p>Organic Pizza Bites. Loaded with Vegetables, Grass-Fed Mozzarella and 10g of Protein. Delicious and Healthy Pizza Bites Made with Organic Ingredients and Zero Empty Calories. Packed with Veggies. Grass-Fed & Free-Range. Zero Empty Calories.</p>

